law.history: Repealed 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 134, sec. 63, effective June 19, 1952. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 1486bb-8.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Challenging voter regarding registration; voting record; registration only prima facie evidence of right to vote.
